Organization Announcement    It is my pleasure to announce that Kenneth Lovejoy has joined Enron Corp. EH&S Asset Operations.
He will be reporting directly to Donnie Willmann and  will support Central America, Caribbean and EES.
Ken has over 25 year experience in environmental, health and safety for the oil and gas industry.
He has been working for Enron since 1996 and has extensive international experience.
We are excited to have Ken in our team so, please welcome Ken in his new role.
Henry  Van

